title: Tisino Mini Jack to Jack Stereo Audio Cable, Nylon Braid 3.5mm to 6.35mm TRS Stereo Jack Cable Interconnect Patch Lead Cord for Guitar, Laptop, Speaker, Amplifiers - 1m
features: 3.5mm to 6.35mm TRS Stereo Cable, this cable has two male connectors, it can communicate in both directions, audio can flow in either direction. This mini-jack to jack cable is designed to interconnect audio devices with 6.35 mm stereo and 3.5 mm stereo. It is ideal for connecting your smartphone, laptop, MP3 players, Tablets, or PC with a 3.5mm jack output to a device with 6.35mm jack inputs such as speakers, mixing consoles, home theater devices, amplifiers, or guitar Amp, etc.

This 6.35mm to 3.5mm adapter cable perfectly combined Heavy-Duty 24K gold-plated 3.5 mm and 6.35 mm connectors, it could eliminate signal loss and static noise, provide durability and improve the signal transmission, and the copper shell blocks any interference which prevents the loss of sound quality.

This AUX to Jack Cable has 20 AWG 4N Oxygen Free Copper to ensure high fidelity sound quality and provide maximum conductivity and signal clarity. a great choice for music lovers, It's especially great for studio or live performances.

3.5mm to 6.35mm Audio Jack Cable--Heavy Duty Flexible Rubber and Nylon Braid Jacket Protect Your Cable, the outer diameter of the jack to mini-jack cable is 6.0mm(0.24 inch), Top quality and made by environment-friendly material, Polyethylene insulation improves high-frequency response, is strong, flexible, and durable.

Flexible TRS cable--Despite multiple layers of shielding and insulation put in place for maximum noise isolation, this cable's construction remains very flexible, doesn't get tangled, and is easy to coil at the end of your gig. It comes with a re-usable velcro strap to keep it organized and tight when not in use.
description: Product Description tisino 3.5mm to 6.35mm Audio Jack Stereo Audio Cable tisino 3.5mm to 1/4 inch TRS Stereo Cable, ideal for connecting between devices with 3.5mm 1/8" and 6.35mm 1/4" port. You can connect your iPod, laptop with 3.5mm jack input to a mixing console, home theater devices, and amplifiers with 6.35mm output. Aux Cable Wide Compatibility 6.35mm 1/4" Male TRS Connect your Mixing Console, Digital Mixer, Mixer, for Behringer XR-8 digital Mixer, for Digital Piano, DVD, home theater Devices, Headphone, Power Amplifiers, Electronic Organ, PA system, Guitar, Speaker, Microphone, Home Stereo Systems, Equalizer, Limiter, BASS, Keyboard, etc. 3.5mm 1/8" Male Connect your standard 3.5mm Aux Jack,such as for MP3 players, Laptops, Computer, CD Players, Cell Phone, Tablets, Home theater, Radio, Speakers, etc. Heavy-duty Components Premium Materials Inside aluminum foil shielding layer to reduce interference, for a better fidelity effect, Cotton Yarn Wrap to reduce noise. Low-Loss 98.5% Copper Braided Spiral-Wound Shield provides maximum cancellation of hum and noise. This full-featured cable has a soft PVC&Nylon jacket for easy use and storage. 4N Oxygen-free copper conductors are encased in bare copper braid shielding to provide pure sound that is noise-free. Features: 3.5mm Gold-Plated Connectors Providing optimal signal transfer and corrosion resistance, The step-down design of the 3.5mm connector provides a connection to recessed ports 6.35mm Gold-Plated Connectors Gold Plated Reinforced Male Plug Delivers Premium Quality Sound with Minimal Interference. Durable and Flexible Cord With a 10000+ bend lifespan several times, high-quality TPE material, and nylon braid externally, this cable really is made to last. Easy to Store Premium metal housing and durable, Free velcro cable wrap included. You Can Use This Cable to... Connect Cell Phone to CD Player Enjoy Music! Great choice for music lovers Connect laptop to Speaker Suitable for device with 3.5mm TRS jack input to device with 6.35mm TRS output. Connect Headphone to Mixer Note： When using a mixer, the device should be connected to the stereo input/output port on the mixer instead of the mono port. Connect E-guitar to PC It's especially great for studio or live performance.
